Name: Pinball Parlor
About the game: A concept anyone can instantly understand. The joy of experiencing a novelty not found in any other game. A game you will want to play again and again after only a short period of time. We have succeeded in these goals by developing this pinball game! With features not found in any other pinball machine, it is a title worthy of the genre once called the King of Games. An entirely new, yet classic play field! It can be played over and over again, with rules both simple and profound! Mind-bogglingly realistic graphics! The ultimate ball and flipper action!
